@@ -0,0 +1,43 @@
+# Phase 2.20 — Route Incident RCA Usefulness Governor
+
+## Цель
+Построить отдельный usefulness governor именно для `route incident RCA`, отдельно от:
+- обычного `operator_rca`
+- `routing incident RCA`
+
+## Что делает
+- использует `quality_score + usefulness_score`
+- строит решения по двум scope:
+  - `action_pattern = action_type + prompt_version + policy_version`
+  - `provider_prompt = provider + model_name + prompt_version`
+- выдаёт только:
+  - `SUPPRESS`
+  - `PROMOTE`
+  - `HOLD`
+
+## Потоки и state
+- `stream:ml:operator_routing_incident_route_rca_governor_decisions`
+- `stream:ml:operator_routing_incident_route_rca_governor_audit`
+- `cfg:ml:operator_routing_incident_route_rca_governor:action:*`
+- `cfg:ml:operator_routing_incident_route_rca_governor:provider:*`
+
+## Safe start
+```bash
+export ML_OPERATOR_ROUTING_INCIDENT_ROUTE_RCA_GOVERNOR_ADVISORY_ONLY=1
+export ML_OPERATOR_ROUTING_INCIDENT_ROUTE_RCA_GOVERNOR_WINDOW_MIN=1440
+export ML_OPERATOR_ROUTING_INCIDENT_ROUTE_RCA_GOVERNOR_MIN_SAMPLE=8
+export ML_OPERATOR_ROUTING_INCIDENT_ROUTE_RCA_GOVERNOR_SUPPRESS_SCORE_MAX=0.45
+export ML_OPERATOR_ROUTING_INCIDENT_ROUTE_RCA_GOVERNOR_PROMOTE_SCORE_MIN=0.72
+```
+
+## Smoke checks
+```bash
+redis-cli XREVRANGE stream:ml:operator_routing_incident_route_rca_governor_decisions + - COUNT 5
+redis-cli XREVRANGE stream:ml:operator_routing_incident_route_rca_governor_audit + - COUNT 5
+redis-cli HGETALL cfg:ml:operator_routing_incident_route_rca_governor:action:open_incident:routing_incident_route_rca_v1:policy_v1
+redis-cli HGETALL cfg:ml:operator_routing_incident_route_rca_governor:provider:vertex:gemini-2.5-flash-lite:routing_incident_route_rca_v1
+curl -s localhost:9905/metrics | grep '^ml_operator_routing_incident_route_rca_governor_'
+```
+
+## Notes
+- scope только `scanner_infra`
+- hot path не затронут
+- advisory-only по умолчанию
diff --git a/orderflow_services/tests/test_operator_routing_incident_route_rca_usefulness_governor_v2_20.py b/orderflow_services/tests/test_operator_routing_incident_route_rca_usefulness_governor_v2_20.py
